snippet.title: Take Over (ft. Jeremy McKinnon (A Day To Remember), MAX, Henry) | Worlds 2020 - League of Legends
snippet.description:
For more information on Worlds 2020 visit http://www.lolesports.com.

Listen now: https://ffm.to/leagueoflegends-takeover
Spotify: https://ffm.to/lol-takeover-spotify
Apple Music: https://ffm.to/lol-takeover-applemusic
YouTube Music: https://ffm.to/lol-takeover-youtubemusic
Deezer: https://ffm.to/lol-takeover-deezer
Amazon Music: https://ffm.to/lol-takeover-amazonmusic


PRODUCTION CREDITS

League of Legends - Take Over
Featured artists: Jeremy McKinnon (A Day To Remember), MAX, and Henry
Written by: Riot Music Team, Alex Seaver of Mako, and Cal Scruby
Mandarin Chinese translation by: Henry and Marshall
Produced by: Riot Music Team
Mixed by: Riot Music Team
Mastered by: Mike Bozzi at Bernie Grundman
Vocals performed by: Jeremy McKinnon (A Day To Remember), MAX, and Henry
Vocal production by: Riot Music Team
 
https://twitter.com/jeremymckinnon 
https://www.instagram.com/maxmusic
https://www.instagram.com/henryl89

Music Video: Created in partnership with The Line Animation
https://www.thelineanimation.com/

-

LYRICS

We at the top again, now what?
Heavy lay the crown, but
Count us 
Higher than the mountain
 
And we be up here for the long run
Strap in for a long one
We got everybody on one
 
Now you're coming at the king so you better not miss
And we only get stronger
With everything I carry up on my back, you should paint it up with a target

Why would you dare me to do it again?
Come get your spoiler up ahead

We're Taking Over, We're Taking Over
Look at you come at my name, you 'oughta know by now
That We're Taking Over, We're Taking Over
Maybe you wonder what you're futures gonna be, but
I got it all locked up

Take a lap, now
Don't be mad, now
Run it back run it back run it back, now
I got bodies lining up, think you're dreaming of greatness?
Send you back home, let you wake up
 
再以后，除了厮杀，这还有其他么？
 (After all, what still exists except for fights)

我左右，键盘噼啪着，时间滴答着    
 (Around me, the keyboard is clicking, the clock is ticking)

还不够，你的固执，让我来守候
 (Still not enough, let me protect your persistence)

哪怕太迟，也不想以后
(Do not worry about the future even if it’s too late)

就在这时，放肆的打斗
(Let out the fight, right at this moment)

I got the heart of lion
I know the higher you climbing, the harder you fall
I’m at the top of the mount
Too many bodies to count, I’ve been through it all
I had to weather the storm to get to level I’m on
That’s how the legend was born
All of my enemies already dead
I’m bored, I’m ready for more
They know I’m ready for war
I told em

We're Taking Over, We're Taking Over
Look at you come at my name, you 'oughta know by now
That We're Taking Over, We're Taking Over
Maybe you wonder what you're futures gonna be, but
I got it all locked up

League of Legends - Take Over
Artistas invitados: Jeremy McKinnon (A Day To Remember), MAX y Henry

Traducción al chino mandarín: Henry y Marshall

Mezcla: Equipo de Riot Music

Voces: Jeremy McKinnon (A Day To Remember), MAX y Henry

https://www.instagram.com/henryl89

—

LETRA

Estamos en la cima, ¿ahora qué?
La corona pesa mucho, pero
Aquí estamos 
Más alto que la montaña
 
Llegamos para quedarnos
Abróchate el cinturón
Todos son parte de este viaje
 
Estás frente al rey, más te vale no fallar
Somos cada vez más fuertes
Con todo el peso en mis hombros me convertí en un blanco

¿Por qué me retas de nuevo?
Aquí te va un spoiler

Estamos dominando, estamos dominando
Mírate, osas enfrentarme, ya deberías saber
Que estamos dominando, estamos dominando
Tal vez no sabes qué traerá el futuro, pero
Ya lo tengo calculado

Ve a dar una vuelta
No te quejes
Da una vuelta, y otra más
Estoy en racha, ¿crees que sueñas con grandeza?
Vuelve a casa, ya despierta
 
再以后，除了厮杀，这还有其他么？
 (Al final, ¿qué hay sino pelear?)

我左右，键盘噼啪着，时间滴答着    
 (A mi alrededor el teclado y el reloj están latiendo)

还不够，你的固执，让我来守候
 (No es suficiente, protegeré tu persistencia)

哪怕太迟，也不想以后
(Que no te angustie el futuro, aunque sea muy tarde)

就在这时，放肆的打斗
(Hay que luchar, el momento es ahora)

Tengo corazón de león
Si escalas muy alto, es más fuerte la caída
Estoy en la cima de la montaña
Estoy en racha, ya perdí la cuenta
Dominé la tormenta para llegar hasta aquí
Así nació la leyenda
Mis enemigos ya están muertos
Me aburrí, quiero más
Saben que a la guerra voy
Se los dije 

Estamos dominando, estamos dominando
Mírate, osas enfrentarme, ya deberías saber
Que estamos dominando, estamos dominando
Tal vez no sabes qué traerá el futuro, pero
Ya lo tengo calculado

PRODUKCE

League of Legends – Převzetí kontroly
Interpreti: Jeremy McKinnon (A Day To Remember), MAX a Henry
Autoři: Hudební tým Riotu, Alex Seaver z Mako a Cal Scruby
Překlad do mandarínské čínštiny: Henry a Marshall
Produkce: Hudební tým Riotu
Mix: Hudební tým Riotu
Mastering: Mike Bozzi ve studiu Bernieho Grundmana
Zpěv: Jeremy McKinnon (A Day To Remember), MAX a Henry
Vokální produkce: Hudební tým Riotu
 
https://twitter.com/jeremymckinnon

https://www.instagram.com/henryl89

https://www.thelineanimation.com/

TEXT

We at the top again, now what?
Heavy lay the crown, but
Count us 
Higher than the mountain
 
And we be up here for the long run
Strap in for a long one
We got everybody on one
 
Now you're coming at the king so you better not miss
And we only get stronger
With everything I carry up on my back, you should paint it up with a target

Why would you dare me to do it again?
Come get your spoiler up ahead

We're taking over, We're Taking Over
Look at you come at my name, you 'oughta know by now
That We're Taking Over, We're Taking Over
Maybe you wonder what you're futures gonna be, but
I got it all locked up

Take a lap, now
Don't be mad, now
Run it back run it back run it back, now
I got bodies lining up, think you're dreaming of greatness?
Send you back home, let you wake up
 
再以后，除了厮杀，这还有其他么？
 (After all, what still exists except for fights)

我左右，键盘噼啪着，时间滴答着    
 (Around me, the keyboard is clicking, the clock is ticking)

还不够，你的固执，让我来守候
 (Still not enough, let me protect your persistence)

哪怕太迟，也不想以后
(Do not worry about the future even if it’s too late)

就在这时，放肆的打斗
(Let out the fight, right at this moment)

I got the heart of lion
I know the higher you climbing, the harder you fall
I’m at the top of the mount
Too many bodies to count, I’ve been through it all
I had to weather the storm to get to level I’m on
That’s how the legend was born
All of my enemies already dead
I’m bored, I’m ready for more
They know I’m ready for war
I told em 

We're taking over, We're Taking Over
Look at you come at my name, you 'oughta know by now
That We're Taking Over, We're Taking Over
Maybe you wonder what you're futures gonna be, but
I got it all locked up

Plus haut que la montagne
 
On est là pour durer
Accrochez-vous bien
On a tout le monde dans le viseur
 
Vous vous attaquez au roi, mieux vaut pas vous rater
On devient plus forts

Pourquoi me mettre au défi de recommencer ?
Attention au spoiler

On prend le contrôle, on prend le contrôle
Regardez-vous viser mon titre, vous devriez le savoir
Qu'on prend le contrôle, on prend le contrôle
Si vous vous demandez ce que sera votre avenir,
Je l'ai mis sous clé

Allez faire un tour,
Soyez pas vexés
On y retourne, on y retourne, on y retourne
Les corps s'alignent, si vous rêvez de grandeur

Je suis au sommet de la montagne
Trop de corps à compter, j'ai déjà tout vu
J'ai résisté à la tempête pour atteindre ce niveau
C'est comme ça qu'est née la légende
Tous mes ennemis sont morts
Je m'ennuie, je veux plus
Ils savent que je suis prêt à me battre
Je les ai prévenus 

On prend le contrôle, on prend le contrôle

Je l'ai mis sous clé

We at the top again, now what?
Heavy lay the crown, but
Count us 
Higher than the mountain

And we be up here for the long run
Strap in for a long one
We got everybody on one

Now you're coming at the king so you better not miss
And we only get stronger
With everything I carry up on my back, you should paint it up with a target

Why would you dare me to do it again?
Come get your spoiler up ahead

We're taking over, We're Taking Over
Look at you come at my name, you 'oughta know by now
That We're Taking Over, We're Taking Over

Maybe you wonder what you're futures gonna be, but
I got it all locked up

Take a lap, now
Don't be mad, now
Run it back run it back run it back, now
I got bodies lining up, think you're dreaming of greatness?
Send you back home, let you wake up
 
再以后，除了厮杀，这还有其他么？
 (After all, what still exists except for fights)

我左右，键盘噼啪着，时间滴答着    
 (Around me, the keyboard is clicking, the clock is ticking)

还不够，你的固执，让我来守候
 (Still not enough, let me protect your persistence)

哪怕太迟，也不想以后
(Do not worry about the future even if it’s too late)

就在这时，放肆的打斗
(Let out the fight, right at this moment)

I got the heart of lion
I know the higher you climbing, the harder you fall
I’m at the top of the mountain
Too many bodies to count, I’ve been through it all
I had to weather the storm to get to level I’m on
That’s how the legend was born
All of my enemies already dead
I’m bored, I’m ready for more
They know I’m ready for war
I told em 

We're Taking Over, We're Taking Over
Look at you come at my name, you 'oughta know by now
That We're Taking Over, We're Taking Over
Maybe you wonder what you're futures gonna be, but
I got it all locked up

LETRA

Estamos en la cima, ¿ahora qué?
La corona pesa mucho, pero
Aquí estamos 
Más alto que la montaña
 
Llegamos para quedarnos
Abróchate el cinturón
Todos son parte de este viaje
 
Estás frente al rey, más te vale no fallar
Somos cada vez más fuertes
Con todo el peso en mis hombros me convertí en un blanco

¿Por qué me retas de nuevo?
Aquí te va un spoiler

Estamos dominando, estamos dominando
Mírate, osas enfrentarme, ya deberías saber
Que estamos dominando, estamos dominando
Tal vez no sabes qué traerá el futuro, pero

No te quejes

哪怕太迟，也不想以后

就在这时，放肆的打斗

Si escalas muy alto, es más fuerte la caída
Estoy en la cima de la montaña
Estoy en racha, ya perdí la cuenta
Dominé la tormenta para llegar hasta aquí
Así nació la leyenda
Mis enemigos ya están muertos
Me aburrí, quiero más
Saben que a la guerra voy
Se los dije 

Estamos dominando, estamos dominando
Mírate, osas enfrentarme, ya deberías saber
Que estamos dominando, estamos dominando
Tal vez no sabes qué traerá el futuro, pero
Ya lo tengo calculado

Deus é a Resposta, ame ele acima de tudo.

Hoje trazemos uma musica que havia sido removida e muito aclamada pelo público que voltasse. A musica foi regravada e complementada.

Beat: Jow Santh
Edição de Vídeo: Jhou Terror
Miniatura do Vídeo: Shouto

Eu prometo continuar melhorando. 
 
Letra:

Se eu me lembrar
Cada vez que você pediu pra eu ficar
Eu neguei mas nada impede de tentar
Ilusão te imagina e você não tá

Nós seguimos juntos, separados por isso
Nada é perfeito e esse meu sacrifício
As palavras que eu nunca teria dito
Então julgue-me, isso nunca foi difícil

Baby, você me deixa
Crazy, no relax my
Problem, me aquece
No sense, a cada frase quente

Problem, me aquece
No sense, a cada frase

Tão à vontade, ela me deixa
A nossa vibe, você vai voltar

A nossa vibe, você vai voltar
Essa saudade, a distância não da
Kimi No Na Wa, Kimi No Na Wa

E ela finge que me esquece, esse é meu perigo
A paciência que talvez nunca tenha tido
E com você isso teria até surgido

A nossa dimensão é a do coração
Te apresentei meu universo e você gostou
É que o destino e a distância separou
Mas dessa vez o multiverso nos juntou

A nossa vibe, você vai voltar

Kimi No Na Wa, Kimi No Na Wa

Não importa o lugar 
Vai está guardado no meu coração 

Your name

Your name

(X2)

Navega no espaço 
Carreguei você no coração

Então me dê a mão 
Dizem que eu perdi pra solidão 
Navego a imensidão como um salto temporal

ABOUT AMERICA'S GOT TALENT
America’s Got Talent," NBC’s No. 1 summer show, returns in May with fresh new faces and familiar favorites, along with the excitement, thrills and feel-good performances that viewers have come to love each season. Creator and Executive Producer Simon Cowell is back at the star-studded judges' table with fan-favorite comedian Howie Mandel. Acclaimed actress and international superstar Sofia Vergara joins as a new judge this season alongside returning judge and global fashion icon Heidi Klum.  The dynamic Terry Crews returns as host. With the show open to acts of all ages, "America's Got Talent" continues to celebrate the variety format like no other show on television. Year after year, "America's Got Talent" features an impressive array of singers, dancers, comedians, contortionists, impressionists, magicians, ventriloquists and hopeful stars, all vying to win America's hearts and a $1 million prize.

America's Got Talent is available now on Peacock, the new streaming service from NBCUniversal. Watch thousands of hours of hit movies and shows, plus daily news, sports, and pop culture updates. Stream now on Peacock.

snippet.title: Se Liga Na Educação - Ciências da Natureza - 17/09/20
snippet.description:
Após as aulas, os vídeos estarão disponíveis no canal: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCTAE3t96gJbgn1K-0yaPV2Q 

O Programa Se Liga na Educação é uma iniciativa da Secretaria de Estado de Educação, apoiada pela Rede Minas e é parte do Regime de Estudo Não Presencial. 

Vai exibir aulas com conteúdos dos diferentes componentes curriculares, divididos por grupos de disciplinas e voltadas para cada ano de escolaridade. O objetivo é levar conteúdos escolares aos alunos da rede pública, neste momento em que as atividades presenciais estão suspensas e as escolas fechadas por causa da pandemia do coronavírus.  

https://estudeemcasa.educacao.mg.gov.br/se-liga-na-educacao

Horário
Vai ao ar de 7h30 a 12h30, de segunda a sexta-feira.

As aulas são posteriormente disponibilizadas separadamente no aplicativo "Conexão Escola" e no canal do YouTube da Secretaria de Estado de Educação (http://youtube.com/estudioeducacaomg).

snippet.title: ♫ O PODER DA VELOCIDADE | FutParódias + Puma
snippet.description:
Uma canção de futebol sobre o incrível poder da velocidade! Pra dibrar sem compaixão e deixar o zagueiro na saudade! O vídeo é parte da parceria entre FutParódias e PUMA e anuncia também o lançamento da chuteira PUMA Ultra!

* Galera, em razão do alto número de vídeos recebidos, a gente vai adiantar o fim do desafio pra amanhã (18/09)! Só assim a gente vai conseguir ser justo e assistir todo mundo que enviou!*

** contém promoção paga

Vídeo gravado na Playball Pompeia.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Letra: Dezão e Leon Whosoever
Produção Musical: Leon Whosoever
Filmagem: Higor Cabral
Edição: Dezão

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

LETRA:

Velocidade é útil pra dibrar sem compaixão
Pra escapar da fúria e do couro de um zagueirão 
E pro estudante

Correr atrás do seu busão

Chega sempre à frente quem dispara igual um louco
Pode alcançar até o pior passe de todos
E se alguém pedir a bola... dá...

Pra ser fominha mais um pouco

O Bolt fica online com o cheirinho das medalha
Um puma fica online na hora da caçada
E eu fico online depois de uma rangada

Com a explosão da feijoada

Falando em Online, agora o Ney é PUMA hein!

Conheça a chuteira que vai te faz correr mais rápido que notícia ruim!
PUMA ULTRA: ULTRA LEVE para uma ULTRA VELOCIDADE
Quer ganhar uma pra você? Quer, não quer?
Tá lançado o Desafio FUTPARÓDIAS e PUMA ULTRA
Grave um TikTok ou um Reels no Instagram com o próximo trecho da música e participe!
Mais detalhes no fim do vídeo!

Lança pros amigo alguma comemoração
Mete uma dancinha num molejo boladão
Para na posição 

Se prepara
PUMA PUMA PUMA PUMA
PUMA ULTRA gingação

É Ultra importante ter um arranque de cavalo
Que faz o time inteiro analisar abobalhado
Quem é o monstro em campo a correr desembestado

Depois de invadir o gramado

snippet.title: Virus-Panik: Droht ein zweiter Lockdown? | Kurzfassung
snippet.description:
Die Langfassung - exklusiv in der #ServusMediathek: https://www.servustv.com/videos/aa-1q676hwq91w11/

▶️▶️  Talk im Hangar-7 - jeden Donnerstag ab 22:10 Uhr bei ServusTV Österreich und Donnerstagnacht bei ServusTV in Deutschland. 

Erst die Schweiz, jetzt auch Deutschland: Immer mehr Nachbarländer sprechen eine Reisewarnung für Wien aus, wo in den letzten Tagen die Zahl der Infektionen stark zunahm. Österreichs Regierung will massiv gegenlenken und berät über weitere Verschärfungen der Corona-Maßnahmen – liegt ein zweiter Lockdown in der Luft? Welche Rolle spielt dabei die Corona-Ampel, von der Kanzler Kurz jetzt sagt, dass sie nurmehr eine bloße Orientierungshilfe sein.

snippet.title: Ruthe.de - FLOSSEN - "Der Streit" (Folge 14)
snippet.description:
Episode 14 der Serie um zwei Dudes mit Kiemen und ihr Leben hinter Glas: Barry und Sting.

Idee, Zeichnungen, Stimmen und Musik: Ralph Ruthe (http://www.ruthe.de)
Animation: Falk (http://www.couchkartoffelsalat.de)

ruthe.de abonnieren: http://bitly.com/ruthede

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Zu Ralph Ruthe:

Ralph Ruthe ist Autor, Musiker, Filmemacher und Cartoonist.
Bereits mit 14 Jahren arbeitete Ruthe als Texter für professionelle Comic-Studios und wurde bald einer der Hauptautoren für Käpt'n Blaubär. Nach seinem Zivildienst veröffentlichte er sein erstes Buch.
1998 begann Ruthe für das MAD-Magazin zu arbeiten, und wurde einer der beliebtesten Zeichner und Autoren.
Seit 2003 konzentriert er sich auf seine Cartoonserie SHIT HAPPENS!, die in vielen Zeitungen und Magazinen in ganz Europa erscheinen. Außerdem arbeitet er regelmäßig an seiner Serie FRÜHREIF, die für eine TV-Umsetzung bearbeitet wurde. 
Von 2005 bis 2008 erhielt er viermal hintereinander für SHIT HAPPENS den Sondermann-Preis der Frankfurter Buchmesse in der Kategorie "Cartoon". 2008 und 2009 gewann der den 1. Preis beim Berliner Kurzfilmfestival "Going Underground".
Mit seiner Multimedia-Comedy-Liveshow tritt er deutschlandweit in ausverkauften Theatern auf.

snippet.title: Take Over (ft. Jeremy McKinnon (A Day To Remember), MAX, Henry) | Worlds 2020 - League of Legends
snippet.description:
For more information on Worlds 2020 visit http://www.lolesports.com.

Listen now: https://ffm.to/leagueoflegends-takeover
Spotify: https://ffm.to/lol-takeover-spotify
Apple Music: https://ffm.to/lol-takeover-applemusic
YouTube Music: https://ffm.to/lol-takeover-youtubemusic
Deezer: https://ffm.to/lol-takeover-deezer
Amazon Music: https://ffm.to/lol-takeover-amazonmusic


PRODUCTION CREDITS

League of Legends - Take Over
Featured artists: Jeremy McKinnon (A Day To Remember), MAX, and Henry
Written by: Riot Music Team, Alex Seaver of Mako, and Cal Scruby
Mandarin Chinese translation by: Henry and Marshall
Produced by: Riot Music Team
Mixed by: Riot Music Team
Mastered by: Mike Bozzi at Bernie Grundman
Vocals performed by: Jeremy McKinnon (A Day To Remember), MAX, and Henry
Vocal production by: Riot Music Team
 
https://twitter.com/jeremymckinnon 
https://www.instagram.com/maxmusic
https://www.instagram.com/henryl89

Music Video: Created in partnership with The Line Animation
https://www.thelineanimation.com/

-

LYRICS

We at the top again, now what?
Heavy lay the crown, but
Count us 
Higher than the mountain
 
And we be up here for the long run
Strap in for a long one
We got everybody on one
 
Now you're coming at the king so you better not miss
And we only get stronger
With everything I carry up on my back, you should paint it up with a target

Why would you dare me to do it again?
Come get your spoiler up ahead

We're Taking Over, We're Taking Over
Look at you come at my name, you 'oughta know by now
That We're Taking Over, We're Taking Over
Maybe you wonder what you're futures gonna be, but
I got it all locked up

Take a lap, now
Don't be mad, now
Run it back run it back run it back, now
I got bodies lining up, think you're dreaming of greatness?
Send you back home, let you wake up
 
再以后，除了厮杀，这还有其他么？
 (After all, what still exists except for fights)

我左右，键盘噼啪着，时间滴答着    
 (Around me, the keyboard is clicking, the clock is ticking)

还不够，你的固执，让我来守候
 (Still not enough, let me protect your persistence)

哪怕太迟，也不想以后
(Do not worry about the future even if it’s too late)

就在这时，放肆的打斗
(Let out the fight, right at this moment)

I got the heart of lion
I know the higher you climbing, the harder you fall
I’m at the top of the mount
Too many bodies to count, I’ve been through it all
I had to weather the storm to get to level I’m on
That’s how the legend was born
All of my enemies already dead
I’m bored, I’m ready for more
They know I’m ready for war
I told em

We're Taking Over, We're Taking Over
Look at you come at my name, you 'oughta know by now
That We're Taking Over, We're Taking Over
Maybe you wonder what you're futures gonna be, but
I got it all locked up

(Hay que luchar, el momento es ahora)

Estoy en la cima de la montaña
Estoy en racha, ya perdí la cuenta
Dominé la tormenta para llegar hasta aquí
Así nació la leyenda
Mis enemigos ya están muertos
Me aburrí, quiero más
Saben que a la guerra voy
Se los dije 

Estamos dominando, estamos dominando
Mírate, osas enfrentarme, ya deberías saber
Que estamos dominando, estamos dominando
Tal vez no sabes qué traerá el futuro, pero
Ya lo tengo calculado

Strap in for a long one
We got everybody on one
 
Now you're coming at the king so you better not miss
And we only get stronger
With everything I carry up on my back, you should paint it up with a target

Why would you dare me to do it again?
Come get your spoiler up ahead

We're taking over, We're Taking Over
Look at you come at my name, you 'oughta know by now
That We're Taking Over, We're Taking Over
Maybe you wonder what you're futures gonna be, but
I got it all locked up

Take a lap, now
Don't be mad, now
Run it back run it back run it back, now
I got bodies lining up, think you're dreaming of greatness?
Send you back home, let you wake up
 
再以后，除了厮杀，这还有其他么？
 (After all, what still exists except for fights)

我左右，键盘噼啪着，时间滴答着    
 (Around me, the keyboard is clicking, the clock is ticking)

还不够，你的固执，让我来守候
 (Still not enough, let me protect your persistence)

哪怕太迟，也不想以后
(Do not worry about the future even if it’s too late)

就在这时，放肆的打斗
(Let out the fight, right at this moment)

I got the heart of lion
I know the higher you climbing, the harder you fall
I’m at the top of the mount
Too many bodies to count, I’ve been through it all
I had to weather the storm to get to level I’m on
That’s how the legend was born
All of my enemies already dead
I’m bored, I’m ready for more
They know I’m ready for war
I told em 

We're Taking Over, We're Taking Over
Look at you come at my name, you 'oughta know by now
That We're Taking Over, We're Taking Over
Maybe you wonder what you're futures gonna be, but
I got it all locked up

Saben que a la guerra voy
Se los dije

Que estamos dominando, estamos dominando
Tal vez no sabes qué traerá el futuro, pero
Ya lo tengo calculado
localizations.it.title: Take Over (ft. Jeremy McKinnon (A Day To Remember), MAX, Henry) | Mondiali 2020 - League of Legends
localizations.it.description:
Per ulteriori informazioni sui Mondiali 2020, visitate il sito http://www.lolesports.com.

Ascolta ora: https://ffm.to/leagueoflegends-takeover
Spotify: https://ffm.to/lol-takeover-spotify
Apple Music: https://ffm.to/lol-takeover-applemusic
YouTube Music: https://ffm.to/lol-takeover-youtubemusic
Deezer: https://ffm.to/lol-takeover-deezer
Amazon Music: https://ffm.to/lol-takeover-amazonmusic


RICONOSCIMENTI PRODUZIONE:

League of Legends - Take Over
Con: Jeremy McKinnon (A Day To Remember), MAX e Henry
Scritto da: Il team musicale di Riot, Alex Seaver dei Mako e Cal Scruby
Traduzione in cinese mandarino: Henry e Marshall
Produzione: Il team musicale di Riot
Missaggio: Il team musicale di Riot
Mastering: Mike Bozzi presso Bernie Grundman Mastering
Cantato da: Jeremy McKinnon (A Day To Remember), MAX e Henry
Produzione vocale: Il team musicale di Riot
 
https://twitter.com/jeremymckinnon 
https://www.instagram.com/maxmusic
https://www.instagram.com/henryl89

Video musicale: creato in collaborazione con The Line Animation
https://www.thelineanimation.com/

-

TESTO

We at the top again, now what?
Heavy lay the crown, but
Count us 
Higher than the mountain
 
And we be up here for the long run
Strap in for a long one
We got everybody on one
 
Now you're coming at the king so you better not miss
And we only get stronger
With everything I carry up on my back, you should paint it up with a target

Why would you dare me to do it again?
Come get your spoiler up ahead

We're taking over, We're Taking Over
Look at you come at my name, you 'oughta know by now
That We're Taking Over, We're Taking Over
Maybe you wonder what you're futures gonna be, but
I got it all locked up

Take a lap, now
Don't be mad, now
Run it back run it back run it back, now
I got bodies lining up, think you're dreaming of greatness?
Send you back home, let you wake up
 
再以后，除了厮杀，这还有其他么？
 (After all, what still exists except for fights)

我左右，键盘噼啪着，时间滴答着    
 (Around me, the keyboard is clicking, the clock is ticking)

还不够，你的固执，让我来守候
 (Still not enough, let me protect your persistence)

哪怕太迟，也不想以后
(Do not worry about the future even if it’s too late)

就在这时，放肆的打斗
(Let out the fight, right at this moment)

I got the heart of lion
I know the higher you climbing, the harder you fall
I’m at the top of the mount
Too many bodies to count, I’ve been through it all
I had to weather the storm to get to level I’m on
That’s how the legend was born
All of my enemies already dead
I’m bored, I’m ready for more
They know I’m ready for war
I told em 

We're Taking Over, We're Taking Over
Look at you come at my name, you 'oughta know by now
That We're Taking Over, We're Taking Over
Maybe you wonder what you're futures gonna be, but
I got it all locked up

snippet.title: Exclusive Behind the Scenes For My New Music Video | Dixie D'Amelio
snippet.description:
This was such a fun shoot with @blackbear and @Lil Mosey I'm so excited for you all to see the official video, but for now, you can just imagine how it turns out! Thanks for watching!

Join me LIVE on @YouTube this Sunday to premiere the official music video!
https://youtu.be/UqO8F-qdo_s

Stream/Buy The New Remix Below:
https://hitco.lnk.to/BeHappyRemix

Subscribe for more official content from Dixie: 
https://www.youtube.com/dixiedamelio?...

Connect with Dixie
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@dixiedamelio
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/dixiedamelio
Twitter: https://twitter.com/dixiedamelio
Website: https://www.dixiedamelio.com

Lyrics

Sometimes I don’t wanna be happy
Don’t hold it against me
If I’m down just leave me there, let me be sad

blackbear
I don't wanna get up outta bed this season 
All bad days, walk away... leave me bleedin
It's fuck you and you
Fuck today, fuck this pain I been feelin
I've got the devil on my shoulder, heart is getting colder 
But, I keep to myself 
Anxiety been creepin', staring at the ceiling
But, I don't need your help 'cause 

Sometimes I don’t wanna be happy
Don’t hold it against me
If I’m down just leave me there, let me be sad
Sometimes I just wanna be lonely
Don’t need you to hold me
If I’m low you don’t need to care, let me be sad
What’s the matter with that?
Oh, oh, oh
What’s the matter with that?
Oh, oh, oh
What’s the matter with…

 Lil Mosey
Sometimes I be by myself 
Cause it feel better 
Sometimes my heart feel like snow
Like it’s cold weather 
I know everyone fake 
I just roll wit it 
So you can’t come with me
If you can’t roll wit us
All of you making me mad
I had to spazz out 
I know it made me feel better 
So I had to cash out 
This fame not what it seems
It brings bad bad energy

 But

Sometimes I don’t wanna be happy
Don’t hold it against me
If I’m down just leave me there, let me be sad
Sometimes I just wanna be lonely
Don’t need you to hold me
If I’m low you don’t need to care, let me be sad
What’s the matter with that?
Oh, oh, oh
What’s the matter with that?
Oh, oh, oh

Bad days, it’s okay
Let me feel it (uh-huh, uh-huh)
In some ways, you’ve gotta break your heart to heal it (heal it)
I’ve got chips on my shoulder, only gettin’ older
So, I keep to myself
Ain’t tryna complain just don’t wanna explain it (explain it)

But

Sometimes I don’t wanna be happy
Don’t hold it against me
If I’m down just leave me there, let me be sad
Sometimes I just wanna be lonely
Don’t need you to hold me
If I’m low you don’t need to care, let me be sad
What’s the matter with that?
Oh, oh, oh
What’s the matter with that?
Oh, oh, oh 
What’s the matter with that?
Oh, oh, oh
What’s the matter with that?
Oh, oh, oh

snippet.title: Für PSG ausnahmsweise mal Rot - Draxler rettet: PSG - Metz 1:0 | Ligue 1 | DAZN Highlights
snippet.description:
Für die Pariser lief es noch nicht richtig in der neuen Saison. In einer interessanten ersten Halbzeit hatten die Gäste aus Metz bessere Chancen. Die zweite Hälfte plätscherte dann eher vor sich hin. Die Ausnahmen: Abdou Diallo. Der will es gleich zwei Mal wissen und steigt zu hart ein. Fazit: Gelb-Rot. Außerdem Draxler, der Schalker Jung köpft zum 1:0.

snippet.title: F.L.Y. & Rookburgh Eröffnungs Video 17.09.2020 - Fly Off Ride Phantasialand Neuheit 2020 Achterbahn
snippet.description:
F.L.Y. & Rookburgh Eröffnungs Video 17.09.2020 - Fly Off Ride Phantasialand Neuheit 2020 Achterbahn FLY hat geöffnet: Erste Eindrücke und Impressionen von der neuen Themenwelt Rookburgh und dem Flying Coaster F.L.Y. im Phantasialand, der am 17.09.2020 Eröffnet wurde.
First impressions of the new theme world Rookburgh and the Flying Coaster F.L.Y. in Phantasialand, which opened on September 17th, 2020.

Eerste indrukken en indrukken van de nieuwe themawereld Rookburgh and the Flying Coaster F.L.Y. in Phantasialand, geopend op 17 september 2020.

Premières impressions et impressions du nouveau monde thématique Rookburgh et le Flying Coaster F.L.Y. à Phantasialand, qui a ouvert le 17 septembre 2020.


Primeras impresiones e impresiones del nuevo mundo temático Rookburgh y Flying Coaster F.L.Y. en Phantasialand, que se inauguró el 17 de septiembre de 2020.


Pierwsze wrażenia i wrażenia z nowego świata tematycznego Rookburgh i Flying Coaster F.L.Y. w Phantasialand, który został otwarty 17 września 2020 roku.


Yeni tema dünyası Rookburgh ve Flying Coaster F.L.Y.'nin ilk izlenimleri ve izlenimleri. 17 Eylül 2020'de açılan Phantasialand'de.


Första intryck och intryck av den nya temavärlden Rookburgh och Flying Coaster F.L.Y. i Phantasialand, som öppnade den 17 september 2020.


Prime impressioni e impressioni del nuovo mondo a tema Rookburgh e del Flying Coaster F.L.Y. a Phantasialand, che ha aperto il 17 settembre 2020.


Первые впечатления и впечатления от нового тематического мира Rookburgh и Flying Coaster F.L.Y. в Phantasialand, который открылся 17 сентября 2020 года.


新しいテーマの世界であるルーバラとフライングコースターF.L.Yの第一印象と印象。 2020年9月17日にオープンしたファンタジアランドで。


新主题世界Rookburgh和Flying Coaster F.L.Y.的第一印象和第一印象 于2020年9月17日开幕的幻想乐园。

snippet.title: PLAYSTATION 5 - Alle Infos: Preis, Release, die Games
snippet.description:
Spiele für Steam, Uplay und Co. jetzt digital bei Gamesplanet.com kaufen: http://bit.ly/2of1MR0 (*)

Am 18. September verriet Sony in einem neuen PS5-Showcase, neben neuen PlayStation-5-Games  endlich auch der Preis und den Release-Termin der PS5. Wir begleiten den Stream live mit unserem Video-Team vorab seht ihr eine reguläre Folge unserer wöchentlichen Live-Show React Live.

Im Stream begrüßen euch Ann-Kathrin Kuhls, Julius Busch und Michael Obermeier.

00:00:00 - Start
00:02:33 - Hat Monster Energy Ubisoft wegen Gods & Monsters verklagt?
00:15:19 - Der beste Controller aller Zeiten? (Zuschauerfrage)
00:26:13 - PS5-Konsolen - Wie viele wurden wirklich hergestellt?
00:29:05 - Jules ist fasziniert von Outer Wilds
00:30:05 - Wann kauft ihr euch neue Grafikkarten?
00:42:18 - Splinter Cell bekommt ein VR-Spiel - Juhu?
00:44:43 - Was ist jetzt eigentlich mit GTA 6?
01:02:14 - Das beste PlayStation Exclusive?
01:18:14 - Was erwarten wir uns vom Showcase?
01:48:43 - Wie viel würdet ihr für die PS5 bezahlen?
02:00:59 - PlayStation 5 Showcase mit neuen Spielen, Preis und Releasedatum
02:48:14 - Nachbesprechung: Was waren unsere Highlights?

In der Nachbesprechung klären wir außerdem noch ein paar Punkte, die während des Showcase nicht erwähnt wurden. Zum Beispiel, ob Demon's Souls und Final Fantasy 16 auch auf dem PC erscheinen - oder sogar auf der PS4?

#GameStar #PS5 #PlayStation 5


***********************************************
PRODUKTPLATZIERUNG / WERBUNG 

Das Video-Team von GameStar & MAX und unser Livestream-Studio wird ausgestattet von RECARO Gaming: http://bit.ly/recaro_gs_special


***********************************************
Über 1.400 exklusive Videos gibt‘s bei GameStar Plus: https://bit.ly/2uU529W

Mehr zur PlayStation 5:
https://www.gamepro.de/artikel/ps5-playstation-5-alle-infos,3340614.html

Folgt uns!
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/GameStar.de
Twitter: http://twitter.com/gamestar_de
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/gamestar.de

 *Hinweis zur Werbung: Gamesplanet.com ist der offizielle PC-Spiele-Partner von GameStar.de und GameStar Plus. Wenn ihr dort Spiele kauft, unterstützt ihr unseren Youtube-Kanal und die GameStar-Website.

Autos | Motorsport | Lifestyle | Vlogs

Ich bin Daniel Abt - professioneller Rennfahrer in der Formel E und die jüngste Generation der Abt Familie. Hier auf meinem Kanal möchte ich dich an meinem Leben teilhaben lassen. #jpperformance

- - -

INSTAGRAM: https://goo.gl/SxiVbk
WEBSITE: http://goo.gl/MPbEzf
- - -
...Jean Pierre Kraemer / JP Performance GmbH - zwei Begriffe die für Spaß, Leistung, Power, freche Sprüche, schnelle Autos, Turbotechnik, Turboumbauten, Ladedruck und noch vieles mehr stehen.
Mit diesen Videos biete ich dir einen Einblick ins tägliche Leben hier in der Firma ,Leistungssteigerungen, technische Details & Erklärungen, Soundfiles, Messwerte, Vergleiche, Neuvorstellungen & Präsentationen und und und...
Du bist quasi "live" bei all unseren Projekten, Events und Reisen in die große, weite Welt mit dabei. Egal ob Audi, BMW, Chrysler, Dodge, Ferrari, Ford, GMC, Honda, Infiniti, Jaguar, Koenigsegg, Lamborghini, Mercedes, Nissan, Opel, Porsche, Range Rover, Skoda, Tesla, Volkswagen oder Wiesmann... es ist für jeden etwas dabei und auch fast von A - Z :-P
Jeder der sich denkt: I LIKE BIG BOOST ist hier genau richtig, frei nach dem Motto FÄHRSTE QUER SIEHSTE MEHR siehst du hier Aufnahmen von Drifts, Drags und anderen Spielerein die große Jungs halt gerne machen.

Wenn du Anregungen / Wünsche oder sonstiges hast, kannst du dich gerne melden unter:

snippet.title: 8 strenge Regeln, die 6ix9ine aktuell befolgen sollte
snippet.description:
Folge uns auf Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/wissenswertyt/

Willkommen bei wissenswert!

Folge uns auf Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/wissenswertYT/

⇨ Geheime Schnäppchen auf Amazon entdecken: https://amzn.to/2W9yUvx


⇨ Bekomme 25€ Rabatt auf deine erste Buchung bei AirBnb: https://goo.gl/r54V62 
⇨ Alle Hörbücher kostenlos hören bei Audible: http://amzn.to/2xQJit1
⇨ Unser Mikrofon: http://amzn.to/2rmaITA  
⇨ Unser Schnittprogramm: http://amzn.to/2q2Mu4M
⇨ iPhone XS günstiger bekommen: https://amzn.to/2RJkTQ6

Anfragen für Kooperationen, Lizenzen, Promotions und ähnliches: 
→ bitte an unsere Business-Email: wissenswert.business@gmail.com

Was ist Wissenswert?
Wie der Name schon sagt, findest du auf Wissenswert allerlei wissenswerten Content, rund um die Themen unserer Zeit – Gesellschaft, Technologie, Wirtschaft, Geschichte, Politik, Stars & Sternchen, YouTube, Life Hacks, Tipps & Tricks, Kurioses, Sport, Wissenschaft und alles, was das Herz begehrt. Aber Wissenswert bedeutet für uns mehr als nur Wissen. Wissenswert ist Infotainment. Wir wollen Spaß und Bildung unter einen Hut bringen, und beides nicht zu kurz kommen lassen, deshalb bringen wir auch regelmäßig Rätsel-Videos oder Game-Show-Formate. Wir wollen unterhalten, wir wollen inspirieren, wir wollen zum Nachdenken anregen und wir wollen Plattform sein, für eine wachsende Community von interessierten und aufgeweckten Menschen. Denn ohne euch, gäb es Wissenswert nicht.

Vielen Dank fürs Angucken! Über Likes, Kommentare und ein Abo würden wir uns riesig freuen!
Wenn du Anregungen, Verbesserungsvorschläge, Videoideen oder Kritik hast, lass es uns wissen! 

Zum Schluss noch ein paar Hinweise: 
→ Auch wenn wir uns bemühen, bestmögliche Recherche zu betreiben, passieren auch uns Fehler. Wir können daher keine Garantie für die faktische Richtigkeit unserer Inhalte übernehmen, daher bitten wir dich, die Informationen in unseren Videos nicht als endgültige Wahrheit aufzufassen.
→ Sollten diskriminierende Meinungen in den Kommentaren zu unseren Videos geäußert werden, wollen wir uns ausdrücklich davon distanzieren. Im Gegenteil, bitten wir alle Zuschauer, trotz der Anonymität des Internets freundlich und respektvoll zu bleiben und diskriminierende Kommentare jeglicher Art zu vermeiden.
→ Mit ⇨ markierte Bereiche können so genannte Affiliate Links sein. Diese Links bringen euch zu Amazon. Wenn du dort etwas über den Link bestellt, unterstützt du Wissenswert ohne mehr zahlen zu müssen.

Impressum: 
→ Weiterleitung: https://wissenswert652465377.wordpress.com/

snippet.title: Zebrakuchen / Marmorkuchen
snippet.description:
Die Mühe lohnt sich, der Zebrakuchen ist ein Blickfang auf dem Kuchenbuffet.

Rezept (26er Springform)

Rührteig
5 Eier
160 g -180 g Zucker
1 P. Vanillezucker (8 g)
200 ml Milch
250 ml Öl
375 g Mehl
1 P. Backpulver (15 g)
2 EL Kakao

Deko
150 g Vollmilchkuvertüre
1 1/2 EL Öl
30 g - 40 g Krokant

Backzeit:
150 ° Umluft ca. 50-55 Minuten

snippet.title: F.L.Y./Rookburgh Soft Opening Phantasialand + First Ride Reaction New Vekoma Flying Coaster
snippet.description:
Our friend Janek (who you may remember from the Japan Coaster Tour) made it out to Phantasialand for the soft opening of their new Vekoma Flying Coaster, F.L.Y.! The ride is the anchor for the new Rookburgh themed area, which has a general aviation/steampunk theme. The entire land has been under construction for 4.5 years, and its finally open!
